type": "APP_IMG_HERO", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974466_2055286774822209_4338361723960595313_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=6tFPWOm5wmwQ7kNvgFGF63m&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAElFMAcJkwuG5Fff7EX1Rya1lJbUfItXXLsRPBNyb0YA&oe=671B87A7"}, {"file_name": "Fluent XR Cover Art.png", "id": "678364797690874", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974640_678364801024207_2897138990588590099_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=-tQlHkeFIFIQ7kNvgF0Ja4B&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAAHHCVyk2YrefQ1pDD-vDRbP7QFCvQn2EyxjF3LrqVPQ&oe=671B8DAB"}, {"file_name": "Fluent XR Logo transparent.png", "id": "212845385153628", "image_type": "APP_IMG_LOGO_TRANSPARENT", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974821_212845391820294_4065972029516719811_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=1-WNhiefI_4Q7kNvgHxJZwe&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYD-tmHJKJg6zcW2HUoPJ57dTyMPr_9DoWZFztZPTVr3gg&oe=671B72D6"}]}, "id": "1137501624009601", "locale": "en_GB", "screenshots": [], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "FluentXR", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Unlock a personalized language learning journey with FluentXR. Using mixed reality passthrough technology, FluentXR transforms your home into an interactive learning space. \n\nStep into a realm where learning is not just fun and effective, but also deeply personalized. FluentXR is not just another language learning app; it's your own private linguistics lab. \n\nTag real-world objects in your space with text and audio labels, making learning immersive and contextually relevant. Dive into our Word Shuffle mini-game to reinforce your skills and beat the timer. \n\nCurrent Features:\nTagging Language: English\nLearning Language: French\nMini-Game: Word Shuffle\n470+ available tags geared towards common living room objects such as \u201cCouch\u201d, \u201cTelevision\u201d, and \u201cGaming Console\u201d\n\nFluentXR is an ever-evolving platform, continually expanding its selection of languages and mini-games. Achieve language mastery with FluentXR\u2014where your home becomes your classroom.", "short_description": "Transform your language learning experience.\n\nUtilizing mixed-reality passthrough technology turn your home into a dynamic classroom. Tag real-world objects in your living room with 470+ customizable tags for learning French. Sharpen your skills through the Word Shuffle mini-game.\n\nFluentXR is an ever-evolving platform, updating with new languages and interactive mini-games. Dive into a context-rich home environment that's both captivating and practical."}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "Fluent XR Cover Art - Portrait.png", "id": "6647755272010080", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_PORTRAIT", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982588_6647755275343413_6975862371154701560_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=uuBEqu8OMSEQ7kNvgFTO-3W&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDghmQ_4cQXZK4EKTEIG185srZGauoBurq35DckBhNc3g&oe=671B9BB4"}, {"file_name": "Fluent XR Mobile Icon.png", "id": "2082304598777986", "image_type": "APP_IMG_ICON", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974858_2082304602111319_6670855186104070571_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=XM1eVOVgRMkQ7kNvgGhNRVX&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBhFvS6jy9e0EjO-cPl2Rac07nBWPSfL55WgBH2hGfHbA&oe=671B84AC"}, {"file_name": "Fluent XR Logo transparent.png", "id": "1984998648546806", "image_type": "APP_IMG_LOGO_TRANSPARENT", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982562_1984998651880139_3178193652368604560_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=pl0mdnptY18Q7kNvgFWn7YE&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYB9rTFn97-L06lypPEUmvyBImraJiQMskcoBMeIvgxgeQ&oe=671B780E"}, {"file_name": "Fluent XR Cover Art.png", "id": "1753372745086018", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974868_1753372748419351_7413283912851125343_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=v7VUC049jTgQ7kNvgFn40Qb&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAyLQCf2D7CtIMjJlqnr8RsuIPWJYNvYgCGrnUSyJOgRg&oe=671B8D75"}, {"file_name": "Fluent XR Cover Art - Square.png", "id": "1307619323205125", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_SQUARE", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75334061_1307619326538458_7751189323196005702_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=trhc6GDdNp0Q7kNvgEWdys8&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYC-S4Homi1MnrY7KeXhyHQ_FTgtGG1Q0fA4okTU06mygg&oe=671B6BB4"}, {"file_name": "Fluent XR Cover Art - Mini Landscape.png", "id": "1239723750053984", "image_type": "APP_IMG_SMALL_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75230044_1239723753387317_7790772509280140276_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=HH4xR00u81kQ7kNvgGtxeLF&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCzbDIplkEjOp2EtUDs2IXkO5_kx9QpLrMot0uzQ3Sfxg&oe=671B8F9E"}, {"file_name": "Fluent XR PDP Art.png", "id": "1061096168226207", "image_type": "APP_IMG_HERO", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75340707_1061096171559540_9065798130022169599_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=Xk8yA_94_aYQ7kNvgE5BB2I&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDkbO5818FcjGK94XfroNKBmeeMoC7JLcczlb-0mt4VGQ&oe=671B9C73"}]}, "id": "449609844722656", "locale": "en_US", "screenshots": [{"file_name": "Sequence 04.00_27_46_18.Still011.png", "id": "755435526614104", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39003240_755435529947437_3157283510711493706_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=Ghs5SP8blL4Q7kNvgFoL7yK&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBqjH9xM-M0kTJW4SiCWse6asKSmzHbYyVEyNatiqCypw&oe=671B89BF"}, {"file_name": "Sequence 04.00_34_53_09.Still016.png", "id": "377326888090872", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031365_377326891424205_2576812618867292544_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=FeVviUBBzYcQ7kNvgHvGENx&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCSV8gGi3Uyt3jDfcaSl-CLK4UVIh4ew7XR_zcI-nZI0w&oe=671B8B8E"}, {"file_name": "Sequence 04.00_49_22_19.Still025.png", "id": "1792607307852843", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39035387_1792607311186176_5280458374548206595_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=velDmB9sPWQQ7kNvgHU4C-_&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCHwf7fCzwmO1ZWNIjBEOPz8G3t2bSSCDFWuFq4T0STGQ&oe=671B9096"}, {"file_name": "Sequence 04.00_52_56_05.Still030.png", "id": "245249301718520", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031325_245249305051853_1598234300064219875_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=LtF7T5UCKAsQ7kNvgFKjNsA&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCcDMoD2kT7Cu8LoYAVPUV89hsnKODrSLE-oi7ZzYMfyQ&oe=671B7037"}, {"file_name": "Sequence 04.00_11_37_00.Still002.png", "id": "733795254815172", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39036675_733795258148505_1346935370172344005_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=VUuYli8q0fMQ7kNvgH7uuX5&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDkc6JYjmzxWKWl553Fg-0m4jG2hXtHBtQVrzu93TZLNA&oe=671B7772"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "Sequence 04.00_27_46_18.Still011.png", "id": "894248482404839", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974686_894248485738172_2991357501924730672_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=b8pmP_lrifcQ7kNvgETjtXf&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBJwNNgrU5n1IztjIKbkdE18-52ITGPIFM0Nt9hVWF10w&oe=671B8F1B"}, "display_name": "FluentXR", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Unlock a personalized language learning journey through your mixed reality home. FluentXR transforms your space into an interactive learning environment.\n\nStep into a realm where learning is not just fun and effective, but also deeply personalized. FluentXR is not just another language learning app; it's your own private linguistics lab.\n\nTag real-world objects in your space with text and audio labels, making learning immersive and contextually relevant. Dive into our Word Shuffle mini-game to reinforce your skills and challenge yourself using the timer.\n\nCurrent Features:\nSpace: Living Room\nMain Language: English\nLearning: French / fran\u00e7ais\nMini-Game: Word Shuffle\n470+ available tags geared towards common living room objects such as \u201cCouch\u201d, \u201cTelevision\u201d, \u201cChess Set\u201d and \u201cGaming Console\u201d\n\nFluentXR is an ever-evolving platform, continually expanding its selection of languages, locations, and mini-games. Achieve language mastery with FluentXR\u2014where your home becomes your classroom.\n\nNext Expansion: \nSpace: Kitchen\nSpace: Bedroom\nMain Language: French\nLearning Language: Spanish / espa\u00f1ol \nLearning Language: English\nMini-Game: Sentence Scramble", "short_description": "Transform your language learning experience. \n\nUtilizing mixed-reality passthrough technology turn your home into a dynamic classroom. Tag real-world objects in your living room with 470+ customizable tags for learning French. Sharpen your skills through the Word Shuffle mini-game.\n\nFluentXR is an ever-evolving platform, updating with new languages, locations, and interactive mini-games. Dive into a context-rich home environment that's both captivating and practical."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://zenfri.ca/fluentxr-privacy-policy/", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "ZenFri Inc.", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://zenfri.ca/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": null, "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873"